  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "网友，你好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "你上班了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "已经10点钟了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:02",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我都要准备下班了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么工作？10点钟就要下班了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "难道你是清洁工吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh你好幽默",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是清洁工，我是老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过老师那么早就下班了吗？你是教什么的老师啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是培训班的老师吗？好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "我早上的课已经上完了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我就觉得等于下班了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是培训班老师，今天周一",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "哪个培训班老师会周一上课？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "有啊，比如那些考公培训班，职业技能的培训班啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "你好好观察细节",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是大学老师。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "原来是大学老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "【失敬失敬】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "小女子这厢有礼了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh什么古风小女子？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "小生不才，未得姑娘青睐",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "【头晕】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "大学老师玩梗也玩的这么溜？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我还不是个老头子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "我才26",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是这个梗都接不上，那不就完了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "那么年轻的大学老师吗？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "【震惊】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，现在一些高校的老师其实都挺年轻的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "不要那么惊讶啦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你是做什么的呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "10点钟就开始找人聊天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "我猜你是上班族",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "废话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是上班族还能干嘛啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "只有上班族和学生两个选项吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "还有失业青年啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "【挠头】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "好吧，那为什么觉得我是上班族呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道10点是大多数白领的上班时间",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "也是开始带薪摸鱼的时间",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh没错",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "我现在就在带薪摸鱼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "好无聊啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也很无聊。在发呆。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我们一起无聊吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你也太无聊了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "还要专门找个人和你一起无聊。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得无聊的时候有人一起陪着，会没那么无聊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "就好像以前读书的时候，班级有那么多人，无聊也变有聊了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "对哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯确实是，以前读书的时候，就算抱怨无聊也没有现在那么无聊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "想回到过去~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "试着用...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "后面我记不住了，接不上",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊，你居然能接上我这个梗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "hh因为我也会无缘无故冒出歌词",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "也期待对方能够接",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "大学老师也这么抽象吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "这种程度不算抽象吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "【蜡笔小新的还好啦】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得挺多，是思维比较发散",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "你在脸红什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有人在夸你啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:23"
    },
    {
      "content": " I啊，因为我这个人天生比较害羞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "【小猫紧张】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "你到底是教什么专业的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "这么的...油腻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "【天塌了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "我以为我这是幽默",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "居然是油腻吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "【嘎巴一下就死了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的很油腻，谁教你这么和女孩子聊天的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我是自学成才",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "完蛋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉这么说更油腻了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "[救命！]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "那还好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "。现在比刚才好点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "心里有数，就显得没那么油腻了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的学生也说过类似的话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "先叠个甲(没有不尊重你，把你当成我学生在装大人的意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我的学生也说过，老师你不装有梗嗯嗯嗯。的时候还挺有梗的，你一旦装的自己很有梗的时候就很尴尬",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你好好的为什么要装有梗呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为想和学生有共同话题啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "希望他们上课的时候能觉得有趣",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "这不是培训班老师该想的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说的是新东方的那种老师吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "为了让学生买课，上课用尽浑身解数",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "对啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "你大学老师还在乎这些吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯嗯。在乎啊。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "不在乎学生觉得上课有没有趣的老师不是好老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是他们觉得上课有趣，我讲的也会更起劲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "，只有老师有趣了，就像是我当学生的时候一样，我希望讲台上老师不但能讲知识，还要讲的有趣",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "你多大呀？感觉你的想法还挺年轻的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "27",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "我操，真那么年轻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然看头像像个老人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是这么年轻的大学老师...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是学霸吗？你是？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "算是吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "就这么承认了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "[凑不要脸]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得你应该也很年轻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么看出来的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "年轻是一种感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以 可以告诉我你多大吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是说不可以呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我就不问了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "I其实我比你大",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "乖乖叫姐姐",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得不像",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是比你大",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "我骗你能有什么好处？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "过过嘴瘾",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "这姐姐你到底叫不叫？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "真叫不出口",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "，太肉麻了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是这类型的，你想找这样的人聊天，你去找这样的吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "乖乖听话，叫姐姐算哪种类型的？你觉得",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是山东人吗？倒装用的好熟练",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "算小奶狗类型的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦，你觉得你不是小奶狗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "完全不是...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你是山东人吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我浙江人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "谁说只有山东人才能倒装句",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "你好，老乡",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也是浙江人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "浙江哪的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "浙江舟山的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "你呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们浙江又不是散装的 都是浙江的就算半个老乡了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "我杭州的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "杭州好啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "我同学也有好多杭州的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "我喜欢吃西湖醋鱼和芭比馒头",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "你味觉失灵了，还是搞抽象了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "搞抽象啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是巴比馒头真的还可以",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "我为芭比馒头发声！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "，本来想说你刻板印象的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "但巴比馒头确实还可以",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "看在巴比馒头的份上就算了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "那真是谢谢你我的包容",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "不对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "是谢谢巴比馒头",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "好无聊啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "你来找点话题，说点有意思的事情吧。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想想",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "今早我去食堂打饭 阿姨要介绍侄女和我相亲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "大学里没有人敢忤逆食堂阿姨",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我又实在不想相亲 我就一边说着嗯嗯，好的一边跑了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是包子落那里了 我又不敢回去拿",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "【苦涩】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "这年头连食堂阿姨都要催婚了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "话说是不是你们大学老师很抢手啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "应该吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "跟我年纪差不多的男同事都早早被内定了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "估计阿姨关心了挺多人的婚恋情况 发现就只有我一个人可以下手，所以对我格外上心了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你为啥没有被内定",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我会拒绝",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "善于拒绝是一种美德",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你为啥要决绝",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "不想结婚吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "拒绝...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "不好意思 我有就错别字的强迫症",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "和你们这些当老师的拼了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "我毕业那么多年，还要给改我的错别字吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "...抱歉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我实在是忍不住",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "不改就手痒",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "【哭哭】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "算了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以为啥拒绝呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "【说话】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "27岁拒绝相亲不是很正常吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "难道你会想去相亲吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "？我才25万，我相什么亲？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "暴露了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "我就觉得你比我小",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "【嘿嘿】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "好奸诈啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "【过奖】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "小生不才 得姑娘谬赞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "【侯明昊古风小生摇扇子】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "笑吐了，古风小生的梗你要玩到什么时候？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真的...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "我蛮喜欢这个梗的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我刚好教的是汉语言文学。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得我用这个梗有很强的自嘲意味，很好玩",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "你教文学的居然爱用这种网络烂梗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "正常来说不应该非常讨厌吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "余华不也会用这些字吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "我普普通通一个大学老师 对文学的追求再高能高得过余华吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "教文学的老师在聊天，学的大家也差不多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯没什么光环，也没什么特别的讲究。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "你这是在立人设吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，为什么会觉得我在立人设呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为你从始至终都好像想展现出一种你不装DE样子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我本来就不装",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你是记者吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉你的风格很犀利",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是在嘲讽我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有嘲讽啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "犀利是褒义词啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得只有善于观察和总结的人才可以犀利",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "比如易立竞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是记者",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "我做新媒体文案的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "也算殊途同归",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你也是学汉语言的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然很多学汉语言的都去搞了文案",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我是学市场营销的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦，那也很契合",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "你倒是说说契合在哪里",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "我自己我自己都没有感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "新媒体文案需要抓住用户痛点吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "必须得了解市场，了解用户，才能写出打动他们的文案",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "市场营销中应该有学这部分吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "讲实话，我自己觉得市场营销是很水的专业",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "过我们的领导教育我们，然后给用户喜欢的东西呀讨好他们",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "创造用户的需求和价值，这确实是市场营销专业里面会讲的东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我写文案的时候逻辑思路还挺跟得上领导的需求的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "反而是那些学派语言文学的看起来专业对口，但事实上就怎么都转不过弯来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为学汉语言学习的是语言本身",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "媒体文案我觉得是会偏广告，新闻学那一类的，所以会有点感汉语言学生的专业思维学习思维",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是这样",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我刚开始去找工作，那些面试的人觉得我不是很合适的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我超级不爽。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，试用期的时候还有实习生是学汉语言的，和我竞争岗位",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "他还觉得自己是专业的，科班出身",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "整天在我面前可拽",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不知道在牛什么，反正最后他也没留下来是我留下来了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "你好像对这个专业的人意见很大？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "有点偏见吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉读了很多书，喜欢咬文嚼字，讲话装装的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还笑得出来？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "我在怼你啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "难道我要生气吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "你确实讲出了部分人的真实现象",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是讲话装装，搞得人牙酸",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "据我的观察，可能是因为读书太多的缘故吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为看过了很多书，见识了很多伟大的人的思想，就是觉得自己也是从中一员看不起没有受过这些熏陶的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我想成为看过很多书，却不会瞧不起别人的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你做到了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "没做到啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "在努力中",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "我经常会因为我认为我的学生应该看过某些书，了解某些想法",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "可是他们却没有",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我会感到有些失望",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你还挺诚实的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "大部分时候真诚一点比较好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "偶尔也很虚伪",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "你们什么时候会比较虚伪呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "举个例子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "突然就开始采访了吗？",
