      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "【气呼呼】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "[贱嗖嗖]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh我们的食堂也没什么好羡慕的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道之前圣诞夜给我们做了什么菜吗？",
