      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "那是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是带薪，我不和你聊天吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "可以告诉我新媒体文案的工作内容了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦其实也没什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是跟热度标题党",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "想办法吸引人来看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么热度都要蹭吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "但最近闹得沸沸扬扬的互联网娱乐圈大点兵蹭了吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我操，你怎么连这都知道？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我又不是个老头子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我用的5g网冲浪 不是2g",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "得跟上学生的步伐",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实主要是我刚发现学生写的提纲乱七八糟",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是她的真实水平",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我去问了才知道原来是他喜欢的明星被点名了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "追谁？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的房也塌了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "檀健次",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "你应该也是檀健次吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我靠，这都被你猜到了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你会算命啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说塌房了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "我冲了一圈浪",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉唯一能够证实塌房的也就只有檀健次了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "【不愿意接受事实】",
