      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也觉得太恶心了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是讨好型人格",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "说檀健次塌了，你就说檀健次恶心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是我说相信他这次 会不会也顺着我说",
